{
  "stem": "14251.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And-- and he said, I have no control, because I stay here just a short time, and I have to move on and then come the next rush of people.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Well, the next rush of people were not the same kind of people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That was-- and they-- they were the Mongolians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "That was another grouping altogether.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It's a whole other ethnic world of Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they did not listen to anyone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "There were no Jews among them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was a-- a fiasco.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we had to walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And that was the grouping of people that divided us, if I remember right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "First of all, they-- they grabbed the 16-year-old Kristal, the daughter who had gotten the pin from my mother, and dragged her screaming out of the place.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The second thing was that the 15 or 14-year-old boy was dragged away, and we never saw either one of them again.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Then they told us to walk a ways and put us up in some other rooms.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I remember my mother was in a bed-- in a bed that was with sheets and all properly made up, and the rest of us were sitting in that same room.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And she was having a terrible gall bladder attack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And in march these people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And-- and we must have been-- I don't know if we had remained there where we were in the first place and we're were just in a different house-- hut thing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I don't know, maybe we were even back in the same one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I see my mother lying there, and these-- these military Russians come in and drag her from her bed in her nightclothes and my mother screaming and yelling.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And-- and we females are all sitting there not knowing what to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
